   Welcome to the Students section of our site. This section includes
   research information about the effects of drug abuse on the brain and
   interactive activities to help you learn more about various drugs and
   how they affect how your brain works. It also features links to
   interesting information about the work that other scientists at the
   National Institutes of Health are doing. Materials in this section are
   public domain and may be reproduced, unless otherwise noted.
